$ Oracle: DBMS_SQL.BIND_VARIABLE
@ dbms_sql.bind_variable

`dbms_sql.bind_variable` associates a → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/statement/bind-variables with a value with which an → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/statement will be executed.

code {
declare
   value  … := …;
begin

   …

   dbms_sql.bind_variable(cur, ':var', value);
   …
end;
/
code }

sa:
  `→ development/databases/Oracle/installed/packages/dbms/sql`
